<Landing
	title="Where MCP security actually lives — and where it doesn't yet — mcp-flowgate"
	description="MCP hands a model a list of tools and trusts it. The security controls that don't fit in a tool definition need a layer of their own — here's what a gateway enforces, and an honest account of what it doesn't."
>

